{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji35.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给刘松林的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给刘松林\"的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1955年8月6日）思齐儿："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信收到。患重感冒，好生休养，恢复体力，以利出国。如今日好些，望来此一看；否则不要来。最要紧是争一口气，学成为国效力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五五、八月六日你要的列宁选集两卷，给你送上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]刘松林，原名刘思齐，1949年同毛泽东的长子毛岸英结婚。1950年毛岸英在抗美援朝战争中牺牲。刘松林这时准备去苏联留学。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1955,"month":8,"day":6}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":275,"page_end":275},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}